Meet Marcy! Marcy is a four month old Calico kitten who just arrived from Red Bluff, CA. She's looking for her new family! She has some anxiety about being left alone, so she'd prefer to be in a home where someone is home most of the day and where she'd have another cat-friendly cat to keep her company.
